name: links
description: For easiest additions, open the PC Part Picker (AU site), copy the part number (only first one if multiple) into the `model` field, for the brand please use the enum `Brands`, for example to do Zotac, type `Brands.ZOTAC`. When adding a new type of card (e.g. 3060 Ti or RX 6800) use the following enum's for the `chipset`: `NVIDIAChipsets.RTX_3060Ti` and `AMDChipsets.RX6800` respectively. For the `card` field, enter the shortest possible descriptor, for example `Eagle OC`, or `FTW3 Ultra Gaming` or `STRIX GAMING` (this is usually what is listed in the list of all graphics cards on PC Part Picker) ___
